268
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:04,960
and He got His realization.

269
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:09,880
So now I am here before you to tell you

270
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:12,720
what is the mechanism.

271
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:18,120
You should not in any case accept Me fully, you should not.

272
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:22,800
