And what you understand through your mind

516
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:58,200
is only the signboard,

517
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:02,240
which you can read; but you have to enter inside,

518
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:06,120
and for that, the ascent has to take place.

519
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,320
That's important.

520
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:11,000
The other day in the university there was only one person

521
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:12,880
who asked many questions.

522
00:35:13,080 --> 00:35:15,280
And he was the one who didn't ascend,

523
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:17,840
the rest of them all ascended.

524
00:35:18,040 --> 00:35:21,240
It's very sad. And we have to work on him, of course;

525
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:24,600
he is going to ascend because he wants to ascend.

526
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:29,640
But the questions went on like that, and such a waste of time.

527
00:35:30,200 --> 00:35:33,800
Because you are earnest seekers and truthful seekers,

528
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:39,280
please ask questions which will help everyone.

529
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:42,480
We have to be kind to everyone.

530
00:35:42,680 --> 00:35:45,680
May God bless you!

531
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:08,840
If you have any questions, please ask Me.

532
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:15,720
Yes?

533
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:18,240
SEEKER: [UNCLEAR], is it dangerous

534
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:22,480
to split a mental cord? [INAUDIBLE]

535
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:30,520
SHRI MATAJI: Now, can you tell Me what he's saying?

536
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:35,160
Just tell it. I'll see, I have to be able to answer.

537
00:36:41,320 --> 00:36:44,080
YOGI: Is it dangerous to split thoughts?

538
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,520
SHRI MATAJI: No, no, no! We are not splitting it.

539
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:51,120
You are sadly mistaken. That's not the point.

540
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:58,000
You see, a thought rises as a reaction to something, all right?

541
00:36:58,200 --> 00:37:02,760
Rises and falls off, and then another thought rises and falls off.

542
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:06,040
In between the thought, there's a little space,

543
00:37:06,240 --> 00:37:09,440
which in Sanskrit called as vilamba.

544
00:37:09,640 --> 00:37:12,920
Now, the thought may come from the future, may come from the past,

545
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:15,960
but when it comes, it goes to the past, all right?

546
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:19,280
Now, what happens: that we see the rising of the thought

547
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:21,600
but not falling of the thought.

548
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:25,600
And in between the thought, this vilamba is the present.

549
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:29,640
Now, if I tell you, “Be in the present,” you cannot.

550
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:33,480
But you just go on thinking, thinking, thinking like mad.

551
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:38,640
On the cusps of the thought you are moving, just like mad.

552
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:42,440
But there's a realm beyond the thought,

553
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:48,000
which is complete awareness and thoughtless awareness,

554
00:37:48,200 --> 00:37:50,240
where there is no thought.

555
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:53,440
And thought is a great joy killer.

556
00:37:53,640 --> 00:37:57,400
I'll tell you how. For example, you are seeing these flowers now.

557
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:59,600
I am also seeing them.

558
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:04,000
Now, I am seeing it thoughtlessly, you are seeing it with thought.

559
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:07,880
So the thought arises: “From what shop She must have bought?

560
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:11,360
How much it must have cost?”

561
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:14,640
Because thought is not joy.

562
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:18,520
But I am just looking at it, without thinking.

563
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:21,040
The complete creation of this,

564
00:38:21,240 --> 00:38:23,960
all the joy that is put into this,

565
00:38:24,160 --> 00:38:26,480
all the joy that has been created by putting it

566
00:38:26,680 --> 00:38:30,480
into this kind of a style, all that is silent

567
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:33,600
is just entering into My being

568
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:38,600
and giving Me that peace and the joy for which it was created.

569
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:42,200
Is a barrier; actually, thought is always a barrier!

570
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:45,360
But when you go beyond thought, it doesn't mean

571
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:49,400
that you cannot think but you become a master.

572
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:52,400
If you want you can think, if you don't want you cannot think.

573
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:56,000
But you are not driven by your thoughts. You see My point?

574
00:38:56,200 --> 00:39:01,040
It's like the thought is riding you, now you ride the thoughts.

575
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:04,560
SEEKER: Can you prevent the thinking?
SHRI MATAJI: Can you…?

576
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:06,320
SEEKER: Can you prevent the thinking I have in my head?

577
00:39:06,520 --> 00:39:09,360
SHRI MATAJI: Yes! If you want, you can just sit silent,

578
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:13,600
in your silence enjoying it. If you want, you can think.

579
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:16,960
But after that, whatever you think

580
00:39:17,160 --> 00:39:21,080
has a special quality.

581
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:26,440
Because that thought that comes to you after your realization

582
00:39:26,640 --> 00:39:30,800
is guided, enlightened by your spirit.

583
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:35,040
Say, a thought comes to you. For example, you are sitting here,

584
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:37,360
and you see something in the darkness,

585
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:39,880
and you think this is a serpent.

586
00:39:40,080 --> 00:39:43,720
For example, you might think; you see, thinking anything is possible.

587
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,520
There's no control.

588
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:48,960
So you think it is a serpent going, and you are frightened of it,

589
00:39:49,160 --> 00:39:52,560
and you try to save yourself. But supposing there is light.

590
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:55,080
Then the same thought tells you, “No, no, it's not,

591
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:57,320
it's just a rope lying there.”

592
00:39:57,520 --> 00:40:01,800
With enlightenment, the same thought has a special quality.

593
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:05,000
Because you see it in all its dimensions and understand

594
00:40:05,200 --> 00:40:09,000
what does that mean, what it is like,

595
00:40:09,200 --> 00:40:14,040
what is the absolute value of particular thought is.

596
00:40:15,040 --> 00:40:17,280
And you just give up.

597
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:21,080
Whatever is not right, you just give up; whatever is right, you accept.

598
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:24,160
Because you see it clearly.

599
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:26,360
So far, there is no discrimination.

600
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:28,960
Now, a thought comes to a person

601
00:40:29,160 --> 00:40:33,800
that “Let me go and murder someone.” This all comes from thought!

602
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:37,960
“Because I hate that person, I must murder that person.” All right?

603
00:40:38,160 --> 00:40:40,040
It's all hatred working.

604
00:40:40,240 --> 00:40:43,520
Now, you may obey that thought, somewhere,

605
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:45,240
and you murder that person.

606
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:49,080
And then, after the violence, the whole thing, the face changes,

607
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:51,840
and you become so nervous, and everything starts.

608
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:54,560
First thought takes you down there to kill the person,

609
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:56,560
and the second thought comes [UNCLEAR]:

610
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:59,800
“Oh God, what have I done!”

611
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:01,640
Both are wrong.

612
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:05,320
But if you are a realized soul, first of all you'll not hate anyone.

613
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:10,840
There are ways of neutralizing the hatred in Sahaja Yoga.

614
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:15,720
And neutralizing even the hatred of the person who hates you.

615
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:18,960
Love's powers we have never known before.

616
00:41:19,160 --> 00:41:21,440
We only know the power of hatred, you see;

617
00:41:21,640 --> 00:41:24,280
the way we are producing MX [MX missile], and this, and that —

618
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:28,280
is nothing, is based on hatred and filth.

619
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:32,240
If these people get realization — I don't know if they'll ever get it —

620
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:34,560
they won't produce all these horrible things,

621
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:39,400
which is making everyone shudder.

622
00:41:39,600 --> 00:41:42,800
We have never used the power of love so far,

623
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:46,080
but that you cannot do it unless and until you have felt it,

624
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:49,280
after realization.

625
00:41:57,320 --> 00:42:00,720
SEEKER: Will you please tell us something of the technique?

626
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:03,920
SHRI MATAJI: Yes, I will.

627
00:42:07,520 --> 00:42:10,480
As I said … that it's a spontaneous thing,

628
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:14,440
it's done as a living process, all right?

629
00:42:14,640 --> 00:42:16,800
Now, say, if I say that …

630
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:20,120
what is the technique of sprouting a seed?

631
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:23,040
That's a living process.

632
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:25,600
No technique, you just put it in the Mother Earth, it sprouts.

633
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:28,320
It's all built in.

634
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:31,520
It's a divine technique,

635
00:42:31,720 --> 00:42:34,480
by which it works out, first.

636
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:38,600
But then you become the master of the technique yourself.

637
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:41,280
Then you can do it!

638
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:46,000
Because you enter into a new realm where you have the divine power,

639
00:42:46,200 --> 00:42:50,920
by which you can do it yourself, you can maneuver it.

640
00:42:51,520 --> 00:42:56,920
But how you get your realization? Is through the spontaneous process.

641
00:42:57,120 --> 00:43:00,400
And a very simple process, is like this: a candle

642
00:43:00,600 --> 00:43:04,760
which is enlightened can enlighten another light.

643
00:43:04,960 --> 00:43:08,160
If the candle is there

644
00:43:08,360 --> 00:43:11,280
and if the candle is in order.

645
00:43:11,480 --> 00:43:15,240
But this candle, if it's a realized soul …

646
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:18,000
that it can also correct —

647
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:21,280
through its techniques, which you have to learn —

648
00:43:21,480 --> 00:43:25,840
through its technique, it can also correct

649
00:43:26,040 --> 00:43:30,400
the other candle which is not yet enlightened,

650
00:43:30,600 --> 00:43:33,000
and then can enlighten.

651
00:43:33,200 --> 00:43:35,640
It can do everything!

652
00:43:35,840 --> 00:43:41,760
But the technique of that is to be understood very easily

653
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:45,760
because you become

654
00:43:45,960 --> 00:43:48,400
a collectively conscious personality.

655
00:43:48,600 --> 00:43:52,840
You become, again I say, you become. You become another personality.

656
00:43:53,040 --> 00:43:57,000
Like an egg becomes a bird. That's how you become.

657
00:43:57,200 --> 00:44:01,280
Then the bird has to just learn how to fly.

658
00:44:01,480 --> 00:44:04,360
But how does a …

659
00:44:04,560 --> 00:44:08,960
what is the technique for the egg to become the bird?

660
00:44:09,160 --> 00:44:15,160
It's just to be put in the warmth of the mother hen.

661
00:44:15,640 --> 00:44:18,920
No technique, it's all built in. That's the divine technique.

662
00:44:19,120 --> 00:44:22,520
But then you learn the divine technique yourself, how to do it.

663
00:44:22,720 --> 00:44:27,560
All right? So then, once you are realized,

664
00:44:27,760 --> 00:44:30,320
by very simple method —

665
00:44:30,520 --> 00:44:34,240
which is our job first of all, the job of the realized souls,

666
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:38,840
like the enlightened light — once that is done for you,

667
00:44:39,040 --> 00:44:42,120
then you have to do for others.

668
00:44:42,320 --> 00:44:43,920
Then you have to learn the technique.

669
00:44:44,120 --> 00:44:46,360
But unless and until you are enlightened,

670
00:44:46,560 --> 00:44:52,200
you cannot do any technique, because there's no power flowing.

671
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:55,720
To start this, you have to put it to the mains, isn't it?

672
00:44:55,920 --> 00:44:58,200
Otherwise no use knowing the technique.

673
00:44:58,400 --> 00:45:03,160
If you don't know how to start the car, no use knowing how to drive.

674
00:45:03,360 --> 00:45:07,360
So let us first start it, and then you will learn the driving.

675
00:45:07,560 --> 00:45:09,440
Answered all right now?

676
00:45:09,640 --> 00:45:12,800
SEEKER: Having started, how long does it take to become realized?

677
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:16,600
SHRI MATAJI: No, you are realized at the start only. To begin with.

678
00:45:16,800 --> 00:45:20,600
It takes hardly any time. You get realization first, in the sense

679
00:45:20,800 --> 00:45:24,560
that you become collectively conscious, you become empowered.

680
00:45:24,760 --> 00:45:28,000
But then … it takes hardly any time for some people,

681
00:45:28,200 --> 00:45:30,880
only six, seven days they can become experts.

682
00:45:31,080 --> 00:45:34,360
That's all, that's sufficient.

683
00:45:34,560 --> 00:45:37,480
Some people take some time,

684
00:45:37,680 --> 00:45:42,280
but depending on what obstructions you have in your centers.

685
00:45:42,480 --> 00:45:45,880
If your centers are obstructed, then it takes little more time.

686
00:45:46,080 --> 00:45:50,000
But if they are not, it doesn't take much time.

687
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:58,640
You become automatically endowed with that technique.

688
00:45:58,840 --> 00:46:01,960
Now here we have at least fifty percent who are Sahaja Yogis.

689
00:46:02,160 --> 00:46:05,560
We call them Sahaja Yogis once they become expert, before that not.

690
00:46:05,760 --> 00:46:08,280
At least fifty percent people sitting here are that.

691
00:46:08,480 --> 00:46:11,680
They're just like you, but there's a difference.

692
00:46:11,880 --> 00:46:14,000
If you see, their faces are glowing,

693
00:46:14,200 --> 00:46:16,760
you won't find any pimples or anything on their faces;

694
00:46:16,960 --> 00:46:22,640
very soft skin, young looking, fresh; eyes are sparkling.

695
00:46:22,840 --> 00:46:24,920
They are over here.

696
00:46:25,120 --> 00:46:27,680
And that's how you become.

697
00:46:27,880 --> 00:46:31,360
You become the masters of yourself. Because you become the spirit!

698
00:46:31,560 --> 00:46:35,200
And spirit is the master because it guides you.

699
00:46:35,400 --> 00:46:39,000
All right? We'll work it out.

700
00:46:39,200 --> 00:46:44,240
That's a very good question! Why? Because you want it.

701
00:46:45,800 --> 00:46:50,400
That's a good question that really helps everyone.

702
00:46:56,360 --> 00:46:59,960
Should we have it now? All right.

703
00:47:00,160 --> 00:47:02,760
You have been requested to take out your shoes for a purpose,

704
00:47:02,960 --> 00:47:06,120
there's nothing to insult you or in any way to trouble you

705
00:47:06,320 --> 00:47:09,560
but to help you all. Because the Mother Earth, you see, helps you.

706
00:47:09,760 --> 00:47:11,840
We have to take the help from the Mother Earth,

707
00:47:12,040 --> 00:47:15,440
so we put our feet on the Mother Earth.

708
00:47:16,360 --> 00:47:19,960
We must know this Mother Earth helps us the most,

709
00:47:20,160 --> 00:47:23,480
so we have to put our feet on the Mother Earth,

710
00:47:23,680 --> 00:47:29,680
without much pressure, little apart, not very close to each other.

711
00:47:30,160 --> 00:47:31,840
All right?

712
00:47:32,040 --> 00:47:36,800
If possible, try to put the whole foot on the Mother Earth,

713
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:38,560
and sit comfortably.

714
00:47:38,760 --> 00:47:41,960
Now, if there is anything tight, you can little bit loosen it.

715
00:47:42,160 --> 00:47:45,200
If it is too tight. I mean, you should never be uncomfortable,

716
00:47:45,400 --> 00:47:47,120
because your attention goes …

717
00:47:47,320 --> 00:47:50,160
if there is any uncomfortable feeling, it goes there.

718
00:47:50,360 --> 00:47:52,520
Also better to take out your spectacles and things

719
00:47:52,720 --> 00:47:54,600
because it also helps your eyesight.

720
00:47:54,800 --> 00:47:57,960
It helps so many things, so better to take out your spectacles.

721
00:47:58,160 --> 00:48:00,920
Keep it safe somewhere, so your attention is not

722
00:48:01,120 --> 00:48:04,800
sort of distracted by it.

723
00:48:07,680 --> 00:48:11,520
It's a very, very simple method which we have to use.

724
00:48:11,720 --> 00:48:14,800
First of all, as I told you — here you can see also —

725
00:48:15,000 --> 00:48:17,640
yesterday I told you that these centers

726
00:48:17,840 --> 00:48:21,120
are represented in our fingertips.

727
00:48:21,320 --> 00:48:24,720
Muhammad Sahib has said: “At the time of resurrection,

728
00:48:24,920 --> 00:48:28,080
your hands will speak.” Very clearly He said it.

729
00:48:28,280 --> 00:48:30,680
And now this what happens: that your fingers,

730
00:48:30,880 --> 00:48:35,320
they have got sympathetic endings here —

731
00:48:35,520 --> 00:48:39,280
that much, of course, the medical science also agrees —

732
00:48:39,480 --> 00:48:43,880
but these actually are your centers here represented.

733
00:48:44,080 --> 00:48:48,280
So — five, six, and seven. Here also five, six, and seven.

734
00:48:48,480 --> 00:48:51,120
On the two sympathetic nervous systems, left and right,

735
00:48:51,320 --> 00:48:52,760
as you see here.

736
00:48:52,960 --> 00:48:55,720
The gross is the left sympathetic nervous system,

737
00:48:55,920 --> 00:48:58,760
but the subtle one is called as the Ida Nadi,

738
00:48:58,960 --> 00:49:04,880
which is the one which caters to our desires.

739
00:49:05,960 --> 00:49:09,720
The another one, on the right-hand side,

740
00:49:09,920 --> 00:49:11,960
is the one called as the Pingala Nadi,

741
00:49:12,160 --> 00:49:17,160
which manifests the gross …

742
00:49:19,520 --> 00:49:20,800
channel

743
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:25,920
which represents the right sympathetic nervous system,

744
00:49:26,120 --> 00:49:30,840
which is responsible for the creativity; is the action.

745
00:49:31,040 --> 00:49:34,760
So one is for the desire — first we desire, and then we act —

746
00:49:34,960 --> 00:49:37,880
so this is for the desire, for emotions,

747
00:49:38,080 --> 00:49:40,960
and the right one is for the action.

748
00:49:41,160 --> 00:49:44,080
So we use these hands gradually

749
00:49:44,280 --> 00:49:49,480
according to the obstructions we have on our different centers.

750
00:49:49,680 --> 00:49:54,080
But first of all we have to put the hands just like this:

751
00:49:54,280 --> 00:49:59,680
little bit open, very comfortably put on your lap;

752
00:49:59,880 --> 00:50:02,120
and you have to close your eyes.

753
00:50:02,320 --> 00:50:06,400
That's very important, you have to close your eyes.

754
00:50:07,960 --> 00:50:13,360
Just opposite of mesmerism. Please close your eyes.

755
00:50:13,560 --> 00:50:18,120
Whatever has to happen will happen inside, not outside.

756
00:50:18,320 --> 00:50:21,880
If I say, “Pay attention to yourself inside,” it's impossible.

757
00:50:22,080 --> 00:50:23,920
But it will happen

758
00:50:24,120 --> 00:50:28,440
when some happening takes place,

759
00:50:28,640 --> 00:50:31,240
and your attention will be attracted inside;

760
00:50:31,440 --> 00:50:36,560
and that happening is the awakening of the Kundalini.

761
00:50:41,560 --> 00:50:44,840
Please don't open your eyes. If our eyes are open,

762
00:50:45,040 --> 00:50:47,880
the Kundalini doesn't rise beyond a certain point.

763
00:50:48,080 --> 00:50:50,640
Sometimes She doesn't want to rise at all.

764
00:50:50,840 --> 00:50:55,880
So just keep your eyes shut and put your hands, fingers open,

765
00:50:56,080 --> 00:51:01,360
little … not upward but downward a little bit.

766
00:51:21,520 --> 00:51:25,040
Now, there's a little bit you have to pay attention to:

767
00:51:25,240 --> 00:51:27,200
don't have to open your eyes,

768
00:51:27,400 --> 00:51:30,760
remember that the left side is the desire.

769
00:51:30,960 --> 00:51:34,360
And the desire is the pure desire

770
00:51:34,560 --> 00:51:38,040
to become one with the Divine.

771
00:51:39,720 --> 00:51:43,400
This is the purest desire, and that is represented

772
00:51:43,600 --> 00:51:46,480
by the Kundalini, by this force,

773
00:51:46,680 --> 00:51:51,080
which is placed in the sacrum bone, or the sacred bone,

774
00:51:51,280 --> 00:51:54,400
in the triangular bone as they call it.

775
00:51:54,600 --> 00:51:57,840
Now, the desire has to be kept fixed;

776
00:51:58,040 --> 00:52:02,440
that means the left hand should to be kept as it is.

777
00:52:03,280 --> 00:52:06,240
Now with the right hand we have to work out

778
00:52:06,440 --> 00:52:11,320
the action of clearing our centers.

779
00:52:11,520 --> 00:52:16,360
First of all, please put your right hand on your heart,

780
00:52:16,560 --> 00:52:18,640
on the left-hand side,

781
00:52:18,840 --> 00:52:23,680
because in the heart resides your spirit.

782
00:52:23,880 --> 00:52:27,560
It's better to put it under the coat.

783
00:52:34,560 --> 00:52:37,560
And just say …

784
00:52:38,360 --> 00:52:41,960
or, we should say, ask a question:

785
00:52:42,880 --> 00:52:45,640
“Mother, am I the spirit?”

786
00:52:45,840 --> 00:52:49,080
Ask the question to Me thrice,

787
00:52:49,280 --> 00:52:53,440
in your heart, ask a question: “Am I the spirit?”

788
00:52:53,640 --> 00:52:56,640
Thrice.

789
00:53:02,400 --> 00:53:04,960
This is an absolute question.

790
00:53:05,160 --> 00:53:08,760
You are! But at this stage you just ask the question.

791
00:53:08,960 --> 00:53:11,440
You are the spirit, no doubt!

792
00:53:11,640 --> 00:53:16,480
But ask the question: “Mother, am I the spirit?”

793
00:53:21,640 --> 00:53:25,280
Put both the legs properly on the ground,

794
00:53:25,480 --> 00:53:28,960
separated from each other little bit.

795
00:53:29,720 --> 00:53:33,600
Now take down this hand

796
00:53:33,800 --> 00:53:38,320
to the left side of your stomach — don't open your eyes —

797
00:53:38,520 --> 00:53:42,920
left side, and press it little bit with your fingers.

798
00:53:43,120 --> 00:53:46,160
Here is the center

799
00:53:46,360 --> 00:53:51,760
of your guide, your master.

800
00:53:53,320 --> 00:53:58,000
Because the spirit is the guide and the master,

801
00:53:58,400 --> 00:54:01,120
and as you have asked Me the question

802
00:54:01,320 --> 00:54:04,000
whether you are the spirit,

803
00:54:04,200 --> 00:54:06,240
you better ask another question here,

804
00:54:06,440 --> 00:54:10,160
saying that “Mother, am I my own master?

805
00:54:10,360 --> 00:54:15,560
Am I my own guru? Am I my own guide?”

806
00:54:23,040 --> 00:54:25,720
Sincerely ask this question please.

807
00:54:25,920 --> 00:54:30,120
Lower down on the stomach, on the left-hand side, lower down.

808
00:54:30,320 --> 00:54:33,160
Yes. And put the left hand towards Me.

809
00:54:33,360 --> 00:54:35,800
Left hand should be towards Me, which is a fixed point,

810
00:54:36,000 --> 00:54:39,600
which is the desire that you want to become.

811
00:54:44,320 --> 00:54:50,320
This question is to be asked ten times, because of Ten Commandments.

812
00:54:52,240 --> 00:54:56,520
Or, there are ten petals to this center.

813
00:55:13,560 --> 00:55:19,080
Now again, raise your right hand to your heart position again,

814
00:55:19,280 --> 00:55:22,200
with your left hand at the same point.

815
00:55:22,400 --> 00:55:27,480
Press it a little bit and, again, with full confidence,

816
00:55:27,680 --> 00:55:30,520
please say for My sake, for your sake

817
00:55:30,720 --> 00:55:33,760
that “Mother, I am the spirit.”

818
00:55:33,960 --> 00:55:36,960
Just assert!

819
00:55:39,440 --> 00:55:43,040
You have to say it twelve times.

820
00:55:44,120 --> 00:55:47,800
“Mother, I am the spirit.”

821
00:56:23,760 --> 00:56:27,600
As the spirit is detached,

822
00:56:27,800 --> 00:56:30,160
is blemishless,

823
00:56:30,360 --> 00:56:33,080
it cannot commit any mistakes,

824
00:56:33,280 --> 00:56:36,040
it cannot have any guilt.

825
00:56:36,240 --> 00:56:40,680
So raise the same hand, right hand — left hand keeping the same way —

826
00:56:40,880 --> 00:56:44,400
to the left-side base of the neck.

827
00:56:44,600 --> 00:56:47,000
To the left-side base of the neck;

828
00:56:47,200 --> 00:56:50,960
it's very important, specially for western people

829
00:56:51,160 --> 00:56:55,240
because they always feel guilty, for nothing at all.

830
00:56:55,440 --> 00:56:58,240
You are not to feel guilty!

831
00:56:58,440 --> 00:57:03,280
So, as you are the spirit, you have to say, “Mother,

832
00:57:03,640 --> 00:57:06,640
I am not guilty.”

833
00:57:07,440 --> 00:57:12,320
You have to say this sixteen times please. “Mother, I am not guilty.”

834
00:57:12,520 --> 00:57:15,800
You are the spirit, and how can spirit be guilty?

835
00:57:16,000 --> 00:57:19,400
Don't feel any guilt about anything whatever you have done,

836
00:57:19,600 --> 00:57:23,080
the past is past. At this moment please say,

837
00:57:23,280 --> 00:57:28,440
“Mother, I am not guilty, because I am the spirit.”

838
00:57:28,640 --> 00:57:31,080
And what is your guilt after all,

839
00:57:31,280 --> 00:57:35,080
compared to the forgiveness of God's love?

840
00:57:35,280 --> 00:57:38,480
Because He's the ocean of forgiveness,

841
00:57:38,680 --> 00:57:41,760
He's the ocean of compassion,

842
00:57:41,960 --> 00:57:45,680
He's the ocean of love.

843
00:57:50,880 --> 00:57:53,760
Now raise the same hand. Put the left hand towards Me,

844
00:57:53,960 --> 00:57:57,480
that is important; you must keep the left hand towards Me on the lap,

845
00:57:57,680 --> 00:58:00,680
fixed.

846
00:58:00,960 --> 00:58:04,840
Say it sixteen times please.

847
00:58:07,120 --> 00:58:10,480
“Mother, I am not guilty.” Please say it with full confidence,

848
00:58:10,680 --> 00:58:16,360
is very important, I tell you. Most of you catch on that center.

849
00:58:24,920 --> 00:58:29,800
Now raise your right hand above

850
00:58:30,000 --> 00:58:32,520
onto your forehead, across.

851
00:58:32,720 --> 00:58:35,720
Just put it there.

852
00:58:36,440 --> 00:58:41,400
At this point, you have to forgive everyone.

853
00:58:41,600 --> 00:58:44,240
Just forgive everyone!

854
00:58:44,440 --> 00:58:47,600
Everyone you have to forgive. Put it across.

855
00:58:47,800 --> 00:58:49,840
Some people say it's difficult.

856
00:58:50,040 --> 00:58:52,800
It's a myth that we do not forgive,

857
00:58:53,000 --> 00:58:56,040
because what do we do when we don't forgive?

858
00:58:56,240 --> 00:59:00,600
So just say, “Mother, I forgive everyone.”

859
00:59:00,800 --> 00:59:04,800
Sincerely please say that “Mother, I really forgive everyone.”

860
00:59:05,000 --> 00:59:06,760
You have to just say it twice.

861
00:59:06,960 --> 00:59:11,800
But it is to be said from your heart, then it will work out.

862
00:59:12,000 --> 00:59:17,040
Now put this hand, after saying that, on top of your head,

863
00:59:17,240 --> 00:59:20,600
at the place where it was soft bone in your childhood,

864
00:59:20,800 --> 00:59:25,080
press it with your palm and just try to turn your head

865
00:59:25,280 --> 00:59:28,080
in a clockwise manner, pressing it.

866
00:59:28,280 --> 00:59:32,200
Just press it and turn it a little bit in the clockwise manner.

867
00:59:32,400 --> 00:59:35,880
Press it with your palm, press it with your palm at the point

868
00:59:36,080 --> 00:59:40,960
where it was soft when you were a child.

869
00:59:41,520 --> 00:59:45,680
At this point, I have to say, I am helpless;

870
00:59:45,880 --> 00:59:50,280
if you do not want to have your realization,

871
00:59:50,480 --> 00:59:53,360
I cannot force it through. Because, as I told you,

872
00:59:53,560 --> 00:59:56,520
you have been given your freedom, which is respected.

873
00:59:56,720 --> 00:59:59,840
So here you have to say, “Mother, I want my realization,

874
01:00:00,040 --> 01:00:01,680
please give me realization.”

875
01:00:01,880 --> 01:00:04,760
Unless and until you say that definitely,

876
01:00:04,960 --> 01:00:08,440
I cannot cross the barrier of your freedom.

877
01:00:08,640 --> 01:00:13,320
So please say it clearly in your heart seven times:

878
01:00:13,520 --> 01:00:18,240
“Mother, please give me my Self-realization.”

879
01:00:18,640 --> 01:00:21,640
Seven times please.

880
01:00:45,640 --> 01:00:49,280
Say it from your heart. Say, it, from, your, heart.

881
01:00:49,480 --> 01:00:52,960
Very sincerely, that's important.

882
01:00:53,240 --> 01:00:56,480
Earnestly you have to say that.

883
01:00:59,520 --> 01:01:04,320
Now raise your hand and see if there is a cool breeze coming out;

884
01:01:04,520 --> 01:01:06,400
or if there is a hot thing coming out:

885
01:01:06,600 --> 01:01:08,440
maybe some people will get heat first.

886
01:01:08,640 --> 01:01:11,320
You can change over the hand and see from the other hand,

887
01:01:11,520 --> 01:01:13,400
and put the right hand towards Me.

888
01:01:13,600 --> 01:01:17,320
You can see if there is a cool breeze coming in,

889
01:01:18,560 --> 01:01:21,560
or a hot breeze coming in.

890
01:01:23,400 --> 01:01:26,400
Why don't you see?

891
01:01:31,640 --> 01:01:33,720
It's there, it's there, it's there!

892
01:01:33,920 --> 01:01:37,080
Put your hand like this, right hand … like this … when … yes …

893
01:01:37,280 --> 01:01:41,000
also … and now you see. It's there? All right, gradually.

894
01:01:41,200 --> 01:01:43,840
Now you turn. Again see another hand.

895
01:01:44,040 --> 01:01:47,400
Just try with another hand, you see?

896
01:01:56,600 --> 01:01:58,840
Again change over and see for yourself.

897
01:01:59,040 --> 01:02:03,480
This will help you to get a balance.

898
01:02:16,800 --> 01:02:18,400
If you are feeling in your head,

899
01:02:18,600 --> 01:02:21,200
then see if you are feeling in your hands as well.

900
01:02:21,400 --> 01:02:25,080
Put your hands towards Me. See now if you are feeling in your hands.

901
01:02:25,280 --> 01:02:30,400
She's got it. You've got it, yes!

902
01:02:36,680 --> 01:02:41,640
If you put up your hands like this — open your eyes —

903
01:02:42,480 --> 01:02:45,480
just like this,

904
01:02:47,080 --> 01:02:49,800
you start feeling it in your hands: a little cool breeze

905
01:02:50,000 --> 01:02:54,600
or a movement downward. Start first feeling it.

906
01:02:54,800 --> 01:02:58,080
Are you? Good, good.

907
01:02:58,280 --> 01:03:02,520
Some of you have a center caught up there.

908
01:03:10,000 --> 01:03:11,400
All right?

909
01:03:11,600 --> 01:03:14,680
Feeling it? Now bring it down and see for yourself

910
01:03:14,880 --> 01:03:17,880
if you are feeling it in your hands.

911
01:03:27,960 --> 01:03:31,280
Mm, very relaxed.

912
01:03:33,120 --> 01:03:35,680
Are you? Good. What about you, sir?

913
01:03:35,880 --> 01:03:38,160
Not yet? We will work out. (To a yogi) Just see…

914
01:03:38,360 --> 01:03:40,720
Now, there are Sahaja Yogis here who are sitting,

915
01:03:40,920 --> 01:03:44,840
who can help you also, those who have not felt it.

916
01:03:46,840 --> 01:03:48,960
It will work out, it is going to work out.

917
01:03:49,160 --> 01:03:52,560
It has worked in this lady: face is changed, looking so much younger.

918
01:03:52,760 --> 01:03:55,600
You too.

919
01:03:55,800 --> 01:03:59,720
What about you now? This gentleman, are you feeling now?

920
01:03:59,920 --> 01:04:02,120
He's got just a Hamsa Chakra, this one.

921
01:04:02,320 --> 01:04:06,360
The one who came to Louise? Not yet?

922
01:04:06,560 --> 01:04:10,200
It's all right, it will work out. Now, don't lose patience.

923
01:04:10,400 --> 01:04:13,600
You must have patience with yourself.

924
01:04:18,080 --> 01:04:22,000
Please close your eyes, just close your eyes.

925
01:04:27,640 --> 01:04:30,640
It's going to work out.

926
01:04:31,880 --> 01:04:35,480
There! Now just watch Me without thinking. Let's see can you do it.

927
01:04:35,680 --> 01:04:38,680
All right?

928
01:04:41,560 --> 01:04:44,560
What about these people?

929
01:04:49,080 --> 01:04:50,240
Aah, that's better!

